---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Affiliate Disclosure" description="SecureAutomation affiliate disclosure and transparency policy.">
  <div class="container" style="padding: 4rem 0; max-width: 800px;">
    <h1>Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
    
    <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> March 3, 2026</p>

    <h2>Overview</h2>
    <p>
      SecureAutomation participates in various affiliate marketing programs. This means that when you click
      on certain links on this website and make a purchase, we may receive a commission at no additional
      cost to you.
    </p>

    <h2>What Are Affiliate Links?</h2>
    <p>
      Affiliate links are special tracking links that allow us to earn a commission when you purchase a
      product or service through our recommendation. These commissions help us keep this site running and
      continue providing valuable content.
    </p>

    <h2>Our Promise</h2>
    <ul style="line-height: 2;">
      <li>✅ We only recommend tools we've personally tested or thoroughly researched</li>
      <li>✅ Our reviews are honest and unbiased</li>
      <li>✅ Affiliate commissions do not influence our editorial judgment</li>
      <li>✅ We clearly mark affiliate links where possible</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Affiliate Programs</h2>
    <p>We currently participate in affiliate programs for:</p>
    <ul style="line-height: 2;">
      <li>HubSpot</li>
      <li>Scalenut</li>
      <li>NordLayer</li>
      <li>Surfshark</li>
      <li>Other AI automation and cybersecurity tools</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Your Trust Matters</h2>
    <p>
      We take transparency seriously. If you have any questions about our affiliate relationships or
      how we select products to recommend, please contact us.
    </p>

    <p style="margin-top: 3rem; color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.9rem;">
      This disclosure is in accordance with the Federal Trade Commission's 16 CFR, Part 255:
      "Guides Concerning the Use of Endorsements and Testimonials in Advertising."
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    margin: 2rem 0 1rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  p {
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }
</style>
